{"word":"ἐξερέω","slug":"ἐξερέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐξερέω1</b></el> <el>(attic <a href='S:contracted, contraction'>contr.</a> <el>-ερῶ</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> of <a href='S:ἐξεῖπον'><el>ἐξεῖπον</el></a>\n<p/><i>I will speak out, tell out, utter aloud</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>: so in <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>ἐξείρηκα</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>; 3rd sg. plup. <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>ἐξείρητο</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>; <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>ἐξειρήσεται</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/> <hr/> <el><b>ἐξερέω2</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to inquire into</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; so in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to inquire of</i> a person, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; and in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to search through</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li250'><b>B. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>: <el>ἐξέρομαι</el><p/></div><el>(ionic <el>-είρομαι</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ερήσομαι</el>) (aor2 <el>-ηρόμην</el>) (<a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <el>-ερέσθαι</el>) </el><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to inquire into</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to inquire of</i> a person, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}